		<div id="comment_body_65539350"><p><div class="quote"><p>If you make it illegal to pay ransomware, what is the business model?</p> </div><p>The business model becomes "wreck havoc on companies that are prohibited by law from paying up, to send a message to other countries to not pass such laws" followed by attacks on companies in those countries, accompanied by a "we've got a deal you can't refuse" ransom-payment offer.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_65539350">

</div>
