		<div id="comment_body_65539110"><p>There will be a popular reaction that goes like "But think of all the damage that will be done when the school/hospital/whatever doesn't pay the ransom!".</p><p>Get real. Continuing on the current path of paying ransoms will only lead to a death spiral where attacks become ever more common due to it being so lucrative. The _only_ solution is to eliminate the source of profits, regardless of the short-term consequences.</p></div>
